  "task_html": "\n<p>Alle Kreisausschnitte haben <strong>r = 8 cm</strong>. Berechne die fehlenden Größen.</p>\n\n<div class=\"ring-grid\">\n\n  <!-- i) α+r gegeben → b und As -->\n  <div class=\"ring-card\">\n    <div class=\"ring-card-label\" style=\"color:#2563eb\">i)</div>\n    <svg viewBox=\"0 0 140 150\" class=\"ring-svg\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n      <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"75\" r=\"55\" fill=\"#f1f5f9\" stroke=\"#cbd5e1\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,2\"/>\n      <path d=\"M70,75 L70.0,20.0 A55,55 0 0,1 125.0,75.0 Z\" fill=\"#bfdbfe\" stroke=\"#2563eb\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n      <path d=\"M70.0,57.0 A18,18 0 0,1 88.0,75.0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#2563eb\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" opacity=\".7\"/>\n      <text x=\"70\" y=\"79\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#2563eb\" font-family=\"monospace\" font-weight=\"bold\">α</text>\n      <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"75\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#2563eb\"/>\n      <line x1=\"70\" y1=\"75\" x2=\"70.0\" y2=\"20.0\" stroke=\"#2563eb\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n      <line x1=\"70\" y1=\"75\" x2=\"125.0\" y2=\"75.0\" stroke=\"#2563eb\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n    </svg>\n    <div class=\"ring-data\">\n      <span style=\"background:#2563eb20;color:#2563eb;font-family:DM Mono,monospace;font-size:12px;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;border:1.5px solid #2563eb40;\">α = 90°</span>\n      <span style=\"background:#2563eb20;color:#2563eb;font-family:DM Mono,monospace;font-size:12px;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;border:1.5px solid #2563eb40;\">r = 8 cm</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"ring-inputs\">\n      <label>b =<input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"12.57\" placeholder=\"? cm\"></label>\n      <label>A<sub>s</sub> =<input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"50.27\" placeholder=\"? cm²\"></label>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- ii) b gegeben → α und As -->\n  <div class=\"ring-card\">\n    <div class=\"ring-card-label\" style=\"color:#16a34a\">ii)</div>\n    <svg viewBox=\"0 0 140 150\" class=\"ring-svg\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n      <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"75\" r=\"55\" fill=\"#f1f5f9\" stroke=\"#cbd5e1\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,2\"/>\n      <path d=\"M70,75 L70.0,20.0 A55,55 0 0,1 117.6,102.5 Z\" fill=\"#bbf7d0\" stroke=\"#16a34a\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n      <path d=\"M70.0,57.0 A18,18 0 0,1 85.6,84.0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#16a34a\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" opacity=\".7\"/>\n      <text x=\"70\" y=\"79\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#16a34a\" font-family=\"monospace\" font-weight=\"bold\">α</text>\n      <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"75\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#16a34a\"/>\n      <line x1=\"70\" y1=\"75\" x2=\"70.0\" y2=\"20.0\" stroke=\"#16a34a\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n      <line x1=\"70\" y1=\"75\" x2=\"117.6\" y2=\"102.5\" stroke=\"#16a34a\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n    </svg>\n    <div class=\"ring-data\">\n      <span style=\"background:#16a34a20;color:#16a34a;font-family:DM Mono,monospace;font-size:12px;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;border:1.5px solid #16a34a40;\">b = 16,76 cm</span>\n      <span style=\"background:#16a34a20;color:#16a34a;font-family:DM Mono,monospace;font-size:12px;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;border:1.5px solid #16a34a40;\">r = 8 cm</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"ring-inputs\">\n      <label>α =<input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"120\" placeholder=\"? °\"></label>\n      <label>A<sub>s</sub> =<input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"67.02\" placeholder=\"? cm²\"></label>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- iii) As gegeben → b und α -->\n  <div class=\"ring-card\">\n    <div class=\"ring-card-label\" style=\"color:#d97706\">iii)</div>\n    <svg viewBox=\"0 0 140 150\" class=\"ring-svg\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n      <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"75\" r=\"55\" fill=\"#f1f5f9\" stroke=\"#cbd5e1\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,2\"/>\n      <path d=\"M70,75 L70.0,20.0 A55,55 0 0,1 108.9,36.1 Z\" fill=\"#fde68a\" stroke=\"#d97706\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n      <path d=\"M70.0,57.0 A18,18 0 0,1 82.7,62.3\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#d97706\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" opacity=\".7\"/>\n      <text x=\"70\" y=\"79\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#d97706\" font-family=\"monospace\" font-weight=\"bold\">α</text>\n      <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"75\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#d97706\"/>\n      <line x1=\"70\" y1=\"75\" x2=\"70.0\" y2=\"20.0\" stroke=\"#d97706\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n      <line x1=\"70\" y1=\"75\" x2=\"108.9\" y2=\"36.1\" stroke=\"#d97706\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n    </svg>\n    <div class=\"ring-data\">\n      <span style=\"background:#d9770620;color:#d97706;font-family:DM Mono,monospace;font-size:12px;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;border:1.5px solid #d9770640;\">A<sub>s</sub> = 25,13 cm²</span>\n      <span style=\"background:#d9770620;color:#d97706;font-family:DM Mono,monospace;font-size:12px;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;border:1.5px solid #d9770640;\">r = 8 cm</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"ring-inputs\">\n      <label>α =<input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"45\" placeholder=\"? °\"></label>\n      <label>b =<input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"6.28\" placeholder=\"? cm\"></label>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- iv) b+As gegeben → r -->\n  <div class=\"ring-card\">\n    <div class=\"ring-card-label\" style=\"color:#9333ea\">iv) <span style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:400\">r gesucht</span></div>\n    <svg viewBox=\"0 0 140 150\" class=\"ring-svg\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n      <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"75\" r=\"55\" fill=\"#f1f5f9\" stroke=\"#cbd5e1\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,2\"/>\n      <path d=\"M70,75 L70.0,20.0 A55,55 0 1,1 15.0,75.0 Z\" fill=\"#f0abfc\" stroke=\"#9333ea\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n      <path d=\"M70.0,57.0 A18,18 0 1,1 52.0,75.0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#9333ea\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" opacity=\".7\"/>\n      <text x=\"70\" y=\"79\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#9333ea\" font-family=\"monospace\" font-weight=\"bold\">α</text>\n      <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"75\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#9333ea\"/>\n      <line x1=\"70\" y1=\"75\" x2=\"70.0\" y2=\"20.0\" stroke=\"#9333ea\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n      <line x1=\"70\" y1=\"75\" x2=\"15.0\" y2=\"75.0\" stroke=\"#9333ea\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n    </svg>\n    <div class=\"ring-data\">\n      <span style=\"background:#9333ea20;color:#9333ea;font-family:DM Mono,monospace;font-size:12px;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;border:1.5px solid #9333ea40;\">b = 37,70 cm</span>\n      <span style=\"background:#9333ea20;color:#9333ea;font-family:DM Mono,monospace;font-size:12px;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;border:1.5px solid #9333ea40;\">α = 270°</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"ring-inputs\">\n      <label>r =<input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"8\" placeholder=\"? cm\"></label>\n      <label>A<sub>s</sub> =<input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"150.80\" placeholder=\"? cm²\"></label>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"check-bar\">\n  <button class=\"btn-check\" onclick=\"checkKreisaus()\">✓ Überprüfen</button>\n  <button class=\"btn-reset\" onclick=\"resetKreisaus()\">↺ Zurücksetzen</button>\n  <span class=\"check-result\" id=\"check-result-kreisaus\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.ring-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:14px;margin-top:16px;}\n.ring-card{background:#fafaf9;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:14px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:8px;}\n.ring-card-label{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:800;align-self:flex-start;}\n.ring-svg{width:120px;height:130px;}\n.ring-data{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;width:100%;}\n.ring-inputs{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;width:100%;}\n.ring-inputs label{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;color:var(--ink2);}\n.ring-inputs .cell-input{flex:1;min-width:0;text-align:right;}\n</style>\n",
  "sol_html": "\n<div class=\"ring-grid\">\n  <div class=\"ring-card\"><div class=\"ring-card-label\" style=\"color:#2563eb\">i)</div>\n    <div style=\"font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;line-height:2;width:100%;\">\n      b = 2·π·8·90/360 ≈ <strong>12,57 cm</strong><br>\n      A<sub>s</sub> = π·64·90/360 ≈ <strong>50,27 cm²</strong>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"ring-card\"><div class=\"ring-card-label\" style=\"color:#16a34a\">ii)</div>\n    <div style=\"font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;line-height:2;width:100%;\">\n      α = b·360/(2·π·r) = 16,76·360/50,27 ≈ <strong>120°</strong><br>\n      A<sub>s</sub> = π·64·120/360 ≈ <strong>67,02 cm²</strong>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"ring-card\"><div class=\"ring-card-label\" style=\"color:#d97706\">iii)</div>\n    <div style=\"font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;line-height:2;width:100%;\">\n      α = A<sub>s</sub>·360/(π·r²) = 25,13·360/201,06 ≈ <strong>45°</strong><br>\n      b = 2·π·8·45/360 ≈ <strong>6,28 cm</strong>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"ring-card\"><div class=\"ring-card-label\" style=\"color:#9333ea\">iv)</div>\n    <div style=\"font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;line-height:2;width:100%;\">\n      r = b·360/(2·π·α) = 37,70·360/(2·π·270) ≈ <strong>8 cm</strong><br>\n      A<sub>s</sub> = π·64·270/360 ≈ <strong>150,80 cm²</strong>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n"
